g.text: Output flag goes high when all three happen:
(1) MET_soar_utc_s is non-zero, otherwise no command has been
received to enable SOAR this way
(2) The current MET_utc_s reaches the desired start time given in
(3) The current MET_utc_s is not more than soarParams.s_max
beyond the start time. The parameter s_max limits the total
time that a SOAR maneuver will take, and so we can exit
the mode at this point, all the action is done.
